\/windows\/\">VeraCrypt<\/a><\/li><\/ul><ul><li>Linux: <a href=\"https:\/\/linux.cn\/article-8184-1.html\">LUKS<\/a> \u6216 <a href=\"https:\/\/securityinabox.org\/zh\/guide\/veracrypt\/windows\/\">VeraCrypt<\/a><\/li><\/ul><ul><li>\u5b89\u5353\uff1a\u8fdb\u5230\u201c\u8bbe\u7f6e\u201d&gt;\u201c\u5b89\u5168\u6027\u201d&gt;\u201c\u52a0\u5bc6\u201d<\/li><\/ul><ul><li>iOS: \u4e00\u65e6\u60a8\u8bbe\u7f6e\u4e86\u5bc6\u7801\uff0ciOS\u8bbe\u5907\u5c31\u4f1a\u88ab\u52a0\u5bc6<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>\u7528\u5f3a\u5bc6\u7801\u6216\u957fPIN\u7801\uff0c\u767b\u5f55\u8bbe\u5907<\/li><li>\u6253\u5f00\u64cd\u4f5c\u7cfb\u7edf\u9632\u706b\u5899\u4e0a\u5f00\u5173\u5e76\u67e5\u770b\u5176\u8bbe\u7f6e (<a href=\"https:\/\/support.microsoft.com\/zh-cn\/office\/%E6%89%93%E5%BC%80%E6%88%96%E5%85%B3%E9%97%AD-microsoft-defender-%E9%98%B2%E7%81%AB%E5%A2%99-ec0844f7-aebd-0583-67fe-601ecf5d774f\">MS Windows<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/support.apple.com\/zh-cn\/HT201642\">Mac OS<\/a>)<\/li><li>\u4f7f\u7528\u9632\u75c5\u6bd2\u4fdd\u62a4&nbsp;<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"has-text-align-center wp-block-heading\">\u9605\u8bfb\u66f4\u591a<\/h3>\n\n\n<div class=\"grid grid-6 post-list\"><article class=\"grid-item aimc-ignore\" aria-label=\"Article: \u95f4\u8c0d\u8f6f\u4ef6\uff1a\u4e70\u5bb6\u3001\u5356\u5bb6\u3001\u9488\u5bf9\u76ee\u6807\u53ca\u5176\u5371\u5bb3\" style=\"aiic:ignore;background-image: url('https:\/\/zh.amnesty.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/AI_surveil_poster_pit-wide_v04-640x400.jpg')\" tabindex=\"0\"><div class=\"grid-content\"><span class=\"grid-itemMeta\"><a href=\"https:\/\/zh.amnesty.org\/category\/region-country\/middle-east-and-north-africa\/\" tabindex=\"0\">\u4e2d\u4e1c\u53ca\u5317\u975e<\/a><\/span><h3 class=\"grid-itemTitle\"><a href=\"https:\/\/zh.amnesty.org\/topic\/technology-and-human-rights\/stopspying\/\" tabindex=\"0\">\u95f4\u8c0d\u8f6f\u4ef6\uff1a\u4e70\u5bb6\u3001\u5356\u5bb6\u3001\u9488\u5bf9\u76ee\u6807\u53ca\u5176\u